To use the model:
1) Make a file for the training data, which should be formatted as follows:

*!* fox
[Fox articles]

*!* cnn
[CNN articles]

Where [Fox articles] and [CNN articles] is the text from some number of articles. 

2) Make a file and insert the text of the article you would like the model to guess the source of. 

3) type "make"
4) type "./m -t [training file] -g [guessing file]"

